# USDT Denominated ATOM (ATOMUSDT) 15-Minute Intervals

This dataset contains time-series data for the ATOM (ATOM) denominated
in USDT (Tether), captured in 15-minute intervals. The data spans from
December 30 to December 31, 2023.

## Usage

``` r
ATOM
```

## Format

An [`xts::xts()`](https://rdrr.io/pkg/xts/man/xts.html)-object with 97
rows and 5 columns,

- index:

  \<[POSIXct](https://rdrr.io/r/base/DateTimeClasses.html)\> The
  time-index

- open:

  \<[numeric](https://rdrr.io/r/base/numeric.html)\> Opening price

- high:

  \<[numeric](https://rdrr.io/r/base/numeric.html)\> Highest price

- low:

  \<[numeric](https://rdrr.io/r/base/numeric.html)\> Lowest price

- close:

  \<[numeric](https://rdrr.io/r/base/numeric.html)\> Closing price

- volume:

  \<[numeric](https://rdrr.io/r/base/numeric.html)\> Trading volume

## Examples

``` r
# Load the dataset
data("ATOM")

# chart
chart(
  ticker = ATOM,
  main = kline(),
  sub = list(volume())
)
```
